\lim_{m\to\infty}F(x_m) = \lim_{m\to\infty}P(X \leq x_m) = P(\lim_{m\to\infty}(X \leq x_m)) = P(\bigcap_{m}(X \leq x_m)) = P(\varnothing) = 0
\lim_{x\to -\infty}F(x) = 0
